{"heading":"Gracious is the Lord, and righteous—Precious in the sight of the Lord is the death of His Saints.","number":116,"verseCount":19,"verses":[[1,["I ",["love",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Love","tg/love"],"."]]]," the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],", because he hath heard my voice ",["and",["clarity-word"]]," my supplications."]],[2,["Because he hath inclined his ear unto me, therefore will I call upon ",["him",["clarity-word"]]," as long as I live."]],[3,["The sorrows of death compassed me, and the ",["pains",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Pain","tg/pain"],"."]]]," of ",["hell",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Damnation","tg/damnation"],"."]]]," gat hold upon me: I found trouble and sorrow."]],[4,["Then called I upon the name of the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],"; O ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],", I beseech thee, deliver my soul."]],[5,["Gracious ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],", and righteous; yea, our God ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," ",["merciful",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG God, Mercy of","tg/god-mercy-of"],"."]]],"."]],[6,["The ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," preserveth the ",["simple",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ps. 19:7","ot/ps/19.7"],"."]]],": I was brought low, and he helped me."]],[7,["Return unto thy rest, O my soul; for the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," hath dealt bountifully with thee."]],[8,["For thou hast ",["delivered",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Deliver","tg/deliver"],"."]]]," my ",["soul",["study-note-ref","b",[["Ps. 56:13","ot/ps/56.13"],"."]]]," from death, mine eyes from tears, ",["and",["clarity-word"]]," my feet from falling."]],[9,["I will walk before the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," in the ",["land",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ps. 27:13","ot/ps/27.13"],"."]]]," of the living."]],[10,["I believed, therefore have I spoken: I was greatly afflicted:"]],[11,["I said in my ",["haste",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Rashness","tg/ras